I graduated from the fashion institute back in 1992. 

Worked in the field for a while. 

Found my way to energy healing and life coaching. 

Learned a lot about working with my future self and realizing that to really move the needle on my goals I needed to quit a few things (drop the party lifestyle and stop putting others’ needs before my own). 

Since learning some hard lessons, I find myself returning to my idea of beauty but this time with a more grounded sense of self. 

I might make these Pro Tips a thing .. we’ll see.
